parsed.plot: DEV: Rance and Talia consummated relationship—Talia's first sexual experience revealed submissive desires and psychological resonance with degradation. Rance used untrained Mage-Gift telekinetically (slammed door, closed curtains)—raw channels caused pain, demonstrated unpredictable power. PEND: How to present formalized connection to Selenay—semi-official arrangement known to Circle but hidden publicly.

entities.c: IDENTITY: Lost virginity to Rance—physical evidence includes breast bite mark. STANCE-Rance: Relationship transformed to sexual/romantic bond. Discovered submissive desires—responds intensely to degradation, being called 'Holderkin bitch/slut,' surrender of control. Psychological shift: found liberation in being dominated after lifetime of carrying responsibility. Breaking command for silence during orgasm revealed limits of control. Begging/self-degradation awakened suppressed aspects tied to Holderkin upbringing she'd rejected. STATE: Empathic shields wavering under intensity—required Rance's mental support to maintain grounding. ARC: Acceptance that unprecedented connection with Rance is personal as well as political—resolved through physical intimacy.

STANCE-Rance: Resigned acceptance of complications he creates. Concern about untrained Mage-Gift use. Maintained physical distance during intimacy but bond prevented complete shielding—experienced intensity of coupling through connection despite withdrawal attempt. STANCE-Talia: Surprised by her response to domination—'discovering parts of herself even I didn't see in memory-merge.' Understanding of her need for surrender after years of responsibility.
